18.description:
We help companies to increase their MRR and avoid involuntary churn using Stripe's infrastructure

We are experts in subscriptions, recurring payments and Stripe Billing.

As Stripe Partners, our goal is for your company to take advantage of this leading finance infrastructure.

We speed up the implementation process, cutting out the learning curve and letting your tech team prioritize your product.

We provide 4 main solutions:

Subscriptions: we add value to your subscription business model, with a full integration of Stripes products (Billing, Payments, Radar) to increase your MRR and decrease your churn

Recurring payments: we automatize the recurring payments of your customers, with several payment methods and an integration in all the recurring payment cycle

Dunning Management app in Pai’s SaaS: our SaaS integrates with Stripe’s ecosystem and it allows companies to have a stronger dunning management strategy in order to recover more failed payments and avoid involuntary churn.

Recurring CFDI in Pai’s SaaS: inside your SaaS, you are able to link every recurring payment with a Mexican invoice CFDI generated automatically. With this integration your customer will receive a CFDI for every automatic payment.
